headline: Booking Holdings (BKNG) Is Down 5.5% After Google Unveils Global AI Travel Booking Expansion
summary: In the past week, Alphabet's Google announced the global expansion of its AI-powered travel features, enabling direct booking of flights and accommodations through advanced tools. This move positions Google as a new and powerful competitor for Booking Holdings, heightening industry concerns over future market share and competitive pressure in the online travel sector.
